{"tid":661142,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[中國又贏] 共享單車$1800/部 貴絕全球","createTime":"2018-05-11T09:54:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-12T07:54:02.000Z","uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"259964b9b05ddc88368ac839821519131ea4397b","tid":661142,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T09:54:15.000Z","msg":"　　2017年8月2日，運營町町單車的南京鐵拜網絡科技有限公司因非法集資、資金鏈斷裂，公司與棲霞工商局失去聯系，因此被納入異常企業經營名錄。<br />\n<br />\n　　根據北京青年報10月31日的報道，町町單車創始人丁偉表示，對於退不了押金的一萬多用戶，仍希望退還錢款，<span style=\"color: red;\">或者每人分到一台成本為1800元的單車</span>。"},{"pid":"105d126907f09299bf641374598c90a6beb518be","tid":661142,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T07:38:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b08f9295574fae4d556fa313863630406a546daf","tid":661142,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T07:54:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/12/155352_fd1070cd8e329f2834478d446047cbd8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F12%2F155352_fd1070cd8e329f2834478d446047cbd8.jpg&h=006bf45b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/12/155400_8236fa996c9f9dfc8c894657bc019757.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F12%2F155400_8236fa996c9f9dfc8c894657bc019757.jpg&h=345987a2&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}